FuncDef: The display dfs-group m-lag up-delay command displays the remaining time in the delay for all M-LAG member interfaces in a DFS group to automatically go Up. The display dfs-group m-lag up-delay command displays the remaining time in the delay for all M-LAG member interfaces in a DFS group to automatically go Up.
